clinical_particulars.therapeutic_indications: A topical anti inflammatory product for the relief of the inflammatory and pruritic manifestations of corticosteroid responsive dermatoses

contraindications.disease: Side effects may include acne like eruptions burning dryness excessive hair growth infection of the skin irritation itching lack of skin colour prickly heat skin inflammation skin loss or softening stretch marks
contraindications.pharmacodynamics: Fluocinonide is a potent glucocorticoid steroid used topically as anti inflammatory agent for the treatment of skin disorders such as eczema It mediates its effects to relieve itching redness dryness crusting scaling inflammation and discomfort associated with inflammatory skin conditions
